 -
  Vehicle One</a></font></div>
  <div id=3DPPTC1 class=3DCTxt style=3D'display:none'><font size=3D2>
  <ul>
   <li>If the vehicle is in a room of spotlights, it will continue moving,
       never pausing.</li>
   <li>Is it restless?<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>Does i=
t not
       like light?</li>
   <ul>
    <li>It is rather stupid since it can not go back to the dark spots.</li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover=3D"Over(this)" onmouseout=3D"Out(this)" onclick=3D"Follow(=
