  style=3D'cursor:hand'>
  <td align=3Dright valign=3Dtop>
  <div class=3DsldNum><font size=3D2>2</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=3DPPTP2 class=3DPTxt><font size=3D2><a
  href=3D"javascript:GoToSld('slide0002.htm');" id=3DPPTL2>Thinking it Over=
 -
  Vehicle Two</a></font></div>
  <div id=3DPPTC2 class=3DCTxt style=3D'display:none'><font size=3D2>
  <ul>
   <li>Do Vehicles IIa and IIb like or dislike light?</li>
   <ul>
    <li>IIa) Is restless like Vehicle I and avoids sources, until it finally
        reaches a place where light is hardly felt.</li>
    <li>IIb) Unlike IIa, it turns toward light and approaches it quickly.</=
li>
   </ul>
   <li>How could you describe IIa?</li>
   <ul>
    <li>cowardly</li>
   </ul>
   <li>IIb?</li>
   <ul>
    <li>aggressive</li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover=3D"Over(this)" onmouseout=3D"Out(this)" onclick=3D"Follow(=
this)"
  style=3D'cursor:hand'>
  <td align=3Dright valign=3Dtop>
  <div class=3DsldNum><font size=3D2>3</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=3DPPTP3 class=3DPTxt><font size=3D2><a
  href=3D"javascript:GoToSld('slide0003.htm');" id=3DPPTL3>Thinking it Over=
 -
  Vehicle Three</a></font></div>
  <div id=3DPPTC3 class=3DCTxt style=3D'display:none'><font size=3D2>
  <ul>
   <li>Do Vehicles IIIa and IIIb like or dislike light?</li>
   <ul>
    <li>IIIa) Loves the light.<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </spa=
n>It
        will seek bright light and stop there.</li>
    <li>IIIb) Although it likes light, it explores and searches for even
        brighter light.</li>
   </ul>
   <li>How could you describe IIIa&#8217;s feelings towards light?</li>
   <ul>
    <li>love</li>
   </ul>
   <li>How about IIIb&#8217;s &#8220;personality&#8221;?</li>
   <ul>
    <li>explorative</li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover=3D"Over(this)" onmouseout=3D"Out(this)" onclick=3D"Follow(=
